➜云南保山：隆阳甜柿喜丰收
http://www.sohu.com/a/425007487_114731	4310
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201016/38a0886646c5481ba9cf334479811b6b.jpeg" width="500" height="288" /></p>
